The Royals actress Elizabeth Hurley, 56, looked incredible in a shimmering pale pink dress at the Breast Cancer Research Foundation's Hot Pink Party on Tuesday evening. Her stunning full-length dress had a plunging neckline. The star is known for her jaw-dropping bikini snaps and enviable figure. The charity event has A-list guests in attendance every year and Liz hosted last year. The actress and model has been the Global Ambassador for The Estée Lauder Companies’ Breast Cancer Campaign for over two decades. She looked elegant at the New York event.       